author: China Insights-SOHTV
description:
Think fake sneakers, knockoff KFC, and bootleg iPhones are just jokes? Think again. Behind China’s massive copycat culture lies a much deeper truth: survival. From YES bags to Obama Fried Chicken, and even pirated cancer drugs and online courses—this video dives into the hilarious, heartbreaking, and eye-opening world of China’s counterfeit economy.

🎒 Knockoff brands
🍔 Bootleg fast food
📚 Pirated education
💊 Life-saving fake medicine

It’s funny… until you realize why it exists.

Subscribe for more stories the mainstream doesn’t show you.
title: From Pineapple Phones to Obama Fried Chicken – China’s Copy Culture Explained
